The entire app is the page source.\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"I wanted to see how far I could go building a notes app using only what modern browsers already provide – no frameworks, no storage APIs, no build step.\r\n\r\n**What it does:**\r\n\r\n- Single HTML file, no deps, 111 loc \r\n- Notes live in the URL hash (shareable links!)\r\n- Auto-compressed with CompressionStream\r\n- Plain-text editor (contenteditable)\r\n- History support\r\n- Page title from first # heading\r\n- Respects light/dark mode\r\n- No storage, cookies, or tracking\r\n\r\nThe entire app is the page source.","submitter_user":"antonmedv","user_is_author":true,"tags":["show","web"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/st1mpl","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/st1mpl/lightest_notes_app_implementation_111"},{"short_id":"a9qem9","created_at":"2025-12-23T01:11:39.000-06:00","title":"NPM Package With 56K Downloads Caught Stealing WhatsApp Messages","url":"https://www.koi.ai/blog/npm-package-with-56k-downloads-malware-stealing-whatsapp-messages","score":3,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"siddhartha_golu","user_is_author":false,"tags":["security"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/a9qem9","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/a9qem9/npm_package_with_56k_downloads_caught"},{"short_id":"u38wjo","created_at":"2025-12-22T22:56:58.000-06:00","title":"Memoization via Representables (2022)","url":"https://iagoleal.com/posts/representable-memoize/","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"abhin4v","user_is_author":false,"tags":["haskell"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/u38wjo","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/u38wjo/memoization_via_representables_2022"},{"short_id":"ldlty4","created_at":"2025-12-22T20:05:38.000-06:00","title":"FreeBSD Closes the Laptop Gap: Year One Project Update","url":"https://freebsdfoundation.org/blog/freebsd-closes-the-laptop-gap-year-one-project-update/","sco